      "text": "This Colombian national was arrested illegally crossing into the United States. She embarked in this incredibly dangerous journey with her two young grandchildren. As she recounts here perilous journey, the truth is revealed. Criminal cartel organizations don’t care about your safety. Do not put your life in the hands of ruthless smugglers. \n \nThe dangers of crossing are real. If you cross illegally, you will be arrested, prosecuted, and deported.\n\n@WhiteHouse @DHSgov @CBP @USBPChiefSDC @USBPChiefELC @USBPChiefYUM @USBPChiefTCA @USBPChiefEPT @USBPChiefBBT @USBPChiefDRT @USBPChiefLRT @USBPChiefRGV",
